.TH "ima_load_data" 9 "ima_load_data" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ima_load_data \- appraise decision based on policy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ima_load_data
.BI "(enum kernel_load_data_id id "  ","
.BI "bool contents "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "id" 12
kernel load data caller identifier
.IP "contents" 12
whether the full contents will be available in a later
call to \fBima_post_load_data\fP.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Callers of this LSM hook can not measure, appraise, or audit the
data provided by userspace.  Enforce policy rules requring a file
signature (eg. kexec'ed kernel image).

For permission return 0, otherwise return -EACCES.
